The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Sachin is among ACCs best
                                                                                                                                                                                                     Sachin is among ACCs best
            A STAFF REPORTER                      
	Calcutta: Sachin Tendulkar was chosen ODI Batsman of the Year 2007 at the inaugural Asian Cricket Council (ACC) awards in Karachi late on Saturday evening.         
	Sunil Gavaskar and Imran Khan were given the Silver Jubilee Legendary Cricketer Award. That Gavaskar and Imran would be honoured was reported by The Telegraph on Saturday.               
	THE AWARD WINNERS         
	 ACC Silver Jubilee Legendary Cricketer Award: Sunil Gavaskar and Imran Khan         
	 Test Batsman of the Year 2007: Kumar Sangakkara         
	 Test Bowler of the Year 2007: Muttiah Muralidharan         
	 ODI Batsman of the Year 2007: Sachin Tendulkar         
	 ODI Bowler of the Year 2007: Fervez Mahroof         
	 Womens Cricketer of the Year 2007: Mithali Raj         
	 Umpire of the Year 2007: Aleem Dar         
	 Lifetime Achievement Award to an administrator: Inderjit Singh Bindra (India)                                                                                                                          
